name: fastobo

raw_meta_yaml:
schema_version: 1

context:
  name: fastobo
  version: 0.13.0

package:
  name: ${{ name | lower }}
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/${{ name[0] }}/${{ name }}/${{ name }}-${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c4548bcfb7f9f87188bf5d8e4c7fd530162707265a8d644ee75259d305cd6964

build:
  number: 2
  script:
    - cargo-bundle-licenses --format yaml --output THIRDPARTY.yml
    - ${{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - if: build_platform != target_platform
      then:
        - python
        - cross-python_${{ target_platform }}
        - maturin >=1,<2

    - ${{ compiler('c') }}
    - ${{ stdlib("c") }}
    - ${{ compiler("rust") }}
    - cargo-bundle-licenses
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - maturin >=1,<2
  run:
    - python

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - fastobo

about:
  license: MIT
  license_file:
    - COPYING
    - THIRDPARTY.yml
  summary: Faultless AST for Open Biomedical Ontologies in Python
  homepage: https://github.com/fastobo/fastobo-py
  documentation: https://fastobo.readthedocs.io

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - althonos
